content: I'm thinking of attending the festival on both days, so I'll probably go for the 2-Day General Admission ticket. I'm really excited to see Billie Eilish and The 1975 perform live again. I've already seen The 1975 at the Merriweather Post Pavilion, but I wouldn't mind seeing them again. Do you know if there are any specific set times or schedules available for the festival?
